THE AVERAGE PERSON JUST STAYS HOME AND DOES WHATEVER THEY NEED TO DO ONLINE BE IT STUDY, WORK, TEACH, RESEARCH WHATEVER. The situation is bad, but society an the masses are actually very orderly and know what they need do, to protect themselves and to protect others.
